Company Overview of Gates Capital Management, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Gates Capital Management, Inc. is an employee owned investment manager. It provides its services to pooled investment vehicles, institutional, and private clients. The firm manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. It also manages funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income, and alternative investment markets across the globe. For its equity investments, the firm invests in event driven situations, special situations, and credit focused equities. For its fixed income investments, it invests in distressed securities and bank debt. Gates Capital Management, Inc. was founded in 1996 and is based in New York City.


